{"about_the_game":"The necromancer simulator is back. Assemble your undead from different body parts, combining the abilities of various fantasy races. Upgrade your tower and give it a unique look. Fight your way through hordes of enemies in a procedurally generated world and take titans under control.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/1_lab_framed.gif?t=1730272815\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Undead with Superpowers</h2>Assemble your undead from the body parts of various fantasy races, unlocking countless combinations of attacks and skills. Give them the ability to overcome obstacles, whether it be towering mountains, full-flowing rivers or lakes of red-hot lava. Under the cover of darkness, your undead are stronger, so do your best to prepare for the dangers of the day.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/2_undead_framed.gif?t=1730272815\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique Necromancer Tower</h2>Upgrade the tower with various add-ons and give it a unique look. Build necro labs for growing body parts and technomagic devices that will give you powerful spells and enhance your undead warriors.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/3_tower_framed.gif?t=1730272815\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Procedurally Generated World</h2>Explore dozens of biomes in a procedurally generated world and view the conquered territories on the map. Use suitable body parts when creating the undead, so that they can handle the high mountains, squelchy swamps and dense forests.\u00a0<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/4_world_framed.gif?t=1730272815\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Attack of Titans</h2>This time you'll have to face new monsters of gigantic size that can easily destroy your tower. But you also have the chance to create titans and fight back.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277320/extras/5_titans_framed.gif?t=1730272815\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"My Rite of Passage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2277320/aef5256e4ebee875e3b23ed09bc0b4a0fc4bc42b.jpg"},{"name":"Martial Feats of Comanche Horsemanship","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2277320/9b66cbfe362d11e0222a3bf5c4ea8e267c62e9c4.jpg"},{"name":"I Thought You Were Stronger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2277320/cd947c456d059695ab5a88cd98f347f82d1abe3c.jpg"},{"name":"Listen with Your Ears, React with Your Face","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2277320/10174aaa06d82ee9fc1b8e79449192455ea4c3bb.jpg"},{"name":"The Dark at the End of the Tunnel","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2277320/5600713ba4b8b18320d3c4a327ad82ae7509287d.jpg"},{"name":"The Very Pulse of the Machine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2277320/9bbe0c11a0b40be46440f3f8d12520d532b8d173.jpg"},{"name":"Where Are You Going, Where Have You Been?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2277320/cd115faeedf5f53059d3f7f45a5a4e7df6b2c0dc.jpg"},{"name":"The Base Violence Necessary for Change","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2277320/ed6db8e336da2b0af1fa0f031b01d02d7692b2d5.jpg"},{"name":"Something Unforgivable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2277320/75311179fd6e6acbe558182ef7621e18b5eb63cd.jpg"},{"name":"Glorious Purpose","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2277320/00301f68c5440a8731613c923fbd867e9f7bd40b.jpg"}],"total":38}